column2: Na Jao Saiyan Chhuda Ke Baiyan
Piya Aiso Jiya Mein Samaya Gayo
Tum Aur Hum Bhool Ke Gham
Zara Nazron Se Kah Do Ji
Door Desh Se Koi Sapera Aaya
Beqarar Karke Hamen Yun Na Jaiye
Chali Gori Pee Se Milan Ko
O Babu O Laila Mausam Dekho Chala
Tum Pukar Lo Tumhara Intezar Hai
Meri Jaan Mujhe Jaan Na Kaho
Gori Gori Raat Hai Taron Ki
Ae Dil Ab Kahin Le Ja
Na Tum Hamen Jano Na Hum
Aaj Ki Raat Piya Dil Na Todo
Chup Hai Dharti Chup Hai Chand
Ek Do Teen Char Aur Panch
Waqt Ne Kiya Kya Haseen Sitam
Hazaar Haathwale Mandir Ke Dwar Khule
Khayalon Mein Kisi Ke Is Tarah
Jane Kahan Mera Jigar Gaya Ji
Rimjhim Ke Tarane Leke Aai Barsaat
Ankhon Mein Tum Dil Mein Tum Ho
De Bhi Chuke Hum Dil Nazrana
Ek Baar Zara Phir Keh Do
Chandan Ka Palna Resham Ko Dori
Ham Bhi Hain Tum Bhi Ho
